plot: Emily is threatened by Gina's growing friendship with Shannon. Tamra and Shannon coach Vicki on how to deal with Kelly on their upcoming trip to Arizona. Kelly deals with family issues, as her brother JR encourages her to fix her estranged relationships with her mom and younger brother. Gina is frustrated by Emily's repeated efforts to convince her to join the Vegas trip. Kelly, Shannon and Tamra get to know Braunwyn's eccentric mom over dinner as they try to convince Kelly to go on the group trip to Arizona.
